Description.SourceString: This is the Ancient Factory, where you can craft items and generate gold. As you progress through the World Map, you'll earn stars for completing missions. Every star you acquire gives you 1 additional production resource in the Ancient Factory. Production refreshes every 12 hours so be sure to collect your items regularly! Upgrade the Factory to increase the amount of gold produced and unlock new goods for manufacture.
